hopobject.body: Which university are you at? orchic substance Whilst we do need people to cover the full shift, if you can only volunteer for a few hours we would still love to hear from you - please let us know your availability when you sign up. Once you have signed up, the Shine team will keep in contact with you in the months before the event. A couple of weeks before the event we will let you know more details about your allocated role and your shift time. You will also receive briefing notes beforehand and a full briefing on event night. You will have a designated manager who will guide and support you at the event.
